top_values: {"Kamen defeated Ebessan to become the first champion.": 1, "Tigers Mask vacated the title to enter the Tennozan 2003 tournament.": 1, "Miracle Man won a 4-Way Match which included Ebessan, Kuishinbo Kamen, and Pero to win the vacant championship.": 1, "Kamen was stripped of the title due to a lack of title defenses.": 1, "Okita-kun won an Eight-Man Battle Royal last eliminating Policeman.": 1}
